description: The ultimate on-the-go food and beverage combo, this lunch cooler and beverage bottle set offers two high quality products that you've come to expect from GENUINE THERMOS BRAND. The foam insulated lunch cooler features an adjustable shoulder strap, exterior pockets for additional storage, a mesh bottle pocket that holds the included vacuum insulated beverage bottle, and a quick access lid that allows access to the interior of the cooler without having to unzip the lid. The 24-ounce beverage bottle features THERMOS vacuum insulation technology to keep beverages hot for up to 18 hours or cold for up to 24 hours, perfect for all day beverage enjoyment. The flip-up, push button lid is easy to operate and includes a locking ring to keep the lid secure during transport. The unique smooth flow lid design helps control the flow of warm beverages.
